    "core": [
      "Leader FACTION: Voice of Command Summary Execution: Once per battle round , at the start of any phase, you can select one friendly ASTRA MILITARUM INFANTRY or ASTRA MILITARUM MOUNTED unit that is Battle-shocked and within 12\" of this model. If you do, one model in that unit is destroyed, and that unit is then no longer Battle-shocked. Political Overwatch: While another OFFICER model is in the same unit as this model, you can re-roll Battle-shock test s taken for that unit."
